name: Time Travel (itch) (Elias Macias)
description:
a game about you going through time. there are 7 levels in total. each level packed with enemies and content!

Also Includes a free Demo!

levels:

Level 1 = city

Level 2 = wild west

Level 3 = imagination dimension

Level 4 = Dungeon

Level 5 = ancient japan

Level 6 = The office

Level 7 = Space

Made with unity

Controls

in the menu go to others and press 'controls'
